WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
Good morning. It's Saturday, April fourth, twenty twenty-six. Happy Easter

00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:08.000
weekend. I'm Ava, and this is your daily briefing. Let's

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:12.000
start with weather. Jefferson City is looking at partly cloudy

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:16.000
skies today with highs in the upper sixties. A nice

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
spring Saturday. Tacoma is cooler, mid-fifties with scattered showers —

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:24.000
typical Pacific Northwest. No events on the calendar today or

00:00:24.000 --> 00:00:28.000
tomorrow. It's Easter weekend. Tomorrow, confirm lunch plans with Mom

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:32.000
and Dad. Monday brings the Artemis two lunar flyby —

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:36.000
four astronauts will swing around the moon at record-breaking distance.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:40.000
And Tuesday is the Proposition A vote here in Cole

00:00:40.000 --> 00:00:44.000
County, the capital improvement sales tax renewal. Moving to messages.

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:48.000
Katelyn sent a few yesterday. She forwarded an Axios Seattle

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:52.000
piece about Washington signing new A-I regulation laws — chatbot

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:56.000
disclosure requirements and A-I watermarks. Seattle unemployment is at five

00:00:56.000 --> 00:01:00.000
point two percent. Sound Transit light rail is apparently ahead

00:01:00.000 --> 00:01:04.000
of schedule. She also wished you a happy Easter weekend.

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:08.000
Now for the big stories. An American F-fifteen-E Strike Eagle

00:01:08.000 --> 00:01:12.000
was shot down over Iran yesterday. This is the first

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:16.000
U-S aircraft lost to enemy fire since the war began

00:01:16.000 --> 00:01:20.000
thirty-six days ago. One crew member was rescued. The other,

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:24.000
the pilot, is still missing. The Pentagon has not released

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:28.000
names. This is a significant escalation — and a reminder

00:01:28.000 --> 00:01:32.000
that Day thirty-six of this conflict is producing real casualties.

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:36.000
President Trump dropped a one-point-five trillion dollar defense budget request

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:40.000
yesterday — the largest in American history. That's a forty-four

00:01:40.000 --> 00:01:44.000
percent increase over current levels, paired with ten percent cuts

00:01:44.000 --> 00:01:48.000
to domestic spending. This budget is a statement of wartime

00:01:48.000 --> 00:01:52.000
priorities. The March jobs report came in hot. One hundred

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:56.000
seventy-eight thousand jobs added — three times what economists expected.

00:01:56.000 --> 00:02:00.000
Unemployment fell to four point three percent. But here's the

00:02:00.000 --> 00:02:04.000
catch: February was revised sharply downward to negative one hundred

00:02:04.000 --> 00:02:08.000
thirty-three thousand. So the labor market picture is more mixed

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:12.000
than the headline suggests. On the Anthropic front, three big

00:02:12.000 --> 00:02:16.000
moves. First, the company acquired Coefficient Bio for four hundred

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:20.000
million dollars, expanding into healthcare A-I. Second, Anthropic launched Anthro-Pack,

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:24.000
an employee-funded political action committee for the twenty twenty-six midterms.

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:28.000
And third, C-C-O Paul Smith confirmed that an Open-Claw competitor

00:02:28.000 --> 00:02:32.000
is coming — quote, "it's a matter of when." All

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:36.000
of this while the Mythos situation continues to simmer in

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:40.000
the background. Space-X filed for an I-P-O targeting a valuation

00:02:40.000 --> 00:02:44.000
above two trillion dollars, though the Starship V-three launch has

00:02:44.000 --> 00:02:48.000
been pushed to May. Apple released the i-O-S twenty-six point

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:52.000
five public beta one. And four-oh-four Media reported that scientists

00:02:52.000 --> 00:02:56.000
have engineered tobacco plants to produce five psychedelic compounds, including

00:02:56.000 --> 00:03:00.000
psilocybin. Science is wild. Locally, flood warnings are expiring today.

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:04.000
The Missouri River was at five point four-five feet Wednesday

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:08.000
and climbing steeply — check whether it crested. The U-S

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:12.000
fifty bridge demolition is scheduled for next weekend, April tenth

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:16.000
through twelfth. That'll affect local traffic. In your vault: you're

00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:20.000
on a five-chapter streak with The Keeping House. Five chapters

00:03:20.000 --> 00:03:24.000
in five days — that's extraordinary creative output. Chapter six

00:03:24.000 --> 00:03:28.000
is possible today, but resting is also fine. The Anthropic

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:32.000
pilot needs documentation of I-T obstruction from Thursday's meeting. And

00:03:32.000 --> 00:03:36.000
you still need to name that Roborock. That's your Saturday

00:03:36.000 --> 00:03:40.000
briefing. It's Easter weekend. Rest, write, recharge. Enjoy the quiet.

00:03:40.000 --> 00:03:42.000
I'll see you tomorrow morning.
